title: Southwest Airlines - available seat miles 2011 to 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing ASMs in billions, containing a total of 9 data points.
Overall ASMs in billions has increased over the Year.
ASMs in billions is slightly increasing from 2011 to 2012, roughly constant from 2012 to 2014, gradually increasing from 2014 to 2017, and lastly roughly constant from 2017 to 2019.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
The highest ASMs in billions, of value 159.8 was reached at Year 2018
Minimum ASMs in billions about 120.58 was reached at Year 2011
